🚀 Streamline your ClickUp workflow directly from Alfred!
This powerful workflow brings ClickUp 2.0 to your fingertips with:
✨ QUICK TASK CREATION (cu) Create tasks with natural language: "cu Review proposal :Check requirements #work @fri !1 +Projects" • Title, description, tags, due dates, priorities, and lists - all in one command • Smart autocomplete for tags and lists • Emoji support for rich task formatting
🔍 INTELLIGENT SEARCH • cus - Search all tasks with fuzzy matching • cuo - View tasks due today or overdue • cul - Find tasks created via Alfred
⚙️ SMART CONFIGURATION (cu:config) • Secure API key storage in macOS Keychain • Easy workspace and project setup • Validation to ensure everything works
🛡️ BUILT FOR PROFESSIONALS • Python 3.9+ for modern macOS compatibility • Enterprise-grade security for API credentials • Blazing fast performance with intelligent caching • Works with ClickUp's latest API v2
📚 For complete documentation, examples, and advanced features: https://github.com/four13co/alfred-clickup-four13/blob/master/README.md
